cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper discusses the evaluation of 3D local feature detection and description techniques for object recognition and registration applications. The paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with feature detection and description. Additionally, the paper also discusses the use of these techniques in robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) applications. Finally, the paper may also be relevant to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it deals with 3D data.
